column2: Normed PV feed in series for 1 kWp installed PV capacity
column3: Heat demand time series inclusive losses of district hetaing network. This demand time series needs to be equal to the thermal energy after the thermal storage in the modelica model
column4: This is the COP of the air source heat pump. It must be identical to the COP of the modelica model.
column5: Maximum thermal power of the air sourced heatpump.
column6: Fixed loss factor related to the thermal capacity of the storage. It can be considered as thermal losses in the empty state e.g. at 50C
column7: Loss factor dependent on the state of charge of the storage. It is related to the thermal capacity of the storage
